Patient Record Integration

When saved:

Automatically create or update the Patient Profile.

Inside Patient Profile create:

New Section

“Fagron Prescriptions”

Store:

* Original PDF
* OCR Text
* Structured Prescription
* Date Created
* Prescribing Physician

Chronological timeline.

⸻

Calendar Integration

Automatically create calendar events.

Event 1

Prescription Created

Date = Prescription Date

⸻

Event 2

Recommended Follow-Up

Date calculated from:

Prescription Duration

Examples:

30-day treatment → follow-up at Day 30

60-day treatment → follow-up at Day 60

90-day treatment → follow-up at Day 90

⸻

Event 3

Refill Reminder

Automatically calculated.

Configurable by admin.

Default:

7 days before expected completion.

